      <div class="title">关于报名注册</div>
      <div class="question">如何报名参加PICMUN 2019？</div>
      <div class="answer">PICMUN 2019只接受团队报名，不接受个人报名。
        每个高校限一个代表团报名，人数不设上限，但本会秘书处将因应具体情况对代表团成员进行筛选。
        每个代表团应有一名领队，由领队统计成员所有信息后通过<a href="http://pkuaimun.com/signup">在线报名系统</a>提交。
        报名完成后，领队会收到确认报名邮件，之后会有代表联系总监告知后续步骤。
        如果您在一周内没有收到通知，请与我们联系。</div>
      <div class="question">How do I register for PICMUN 2019?</div>
      <div class="answer">PICMUN 2019 only accepts team applications. Each university should have only one team, but there is no limit to the number of delegates. However, the Secretariat may need to screen the delegates under specific circumstances. Each team should have one Head Delegate who is expected to handle with follow-up matters. The Head Delegate should input all delegates’ information in the online application form accurately and promptly, which can be found at <a href="http://pkuaimun.com/signup">http://pkuaimun.com/signup</a>. A confirmation email will be sent to the Head Delegate and the Director of Delegate Liaison will inform the follow-up matters. Do contact us regarding your application if you have not heard from us within a week.</div>
      <div class="question">领队需要先注册本会官方网站账号吗？</div>
      <div class="answer">是的。各代表团领队须先在本会官方网站上注册账号，账号注册审核将于三个工作日内完成。届时领队可登入系统进行报名申请。请各领队预留账号申请的审核时间，避免错过报名期限。</div>      
      <div class="question">Does the Head Delegate have to create an account before applying for registration?</div>
      <div class="answer">Yes. To register for PICMUN 2019, the Head Delegate is required to create an account on our official website. The review of account registration will be completed within three working days. Then the Head Delegate will be able to log in to the system to apply for registration. Please set aside enough time for the review in case you miss the registration deadline.</div>     
      <div class="question">领队需要代表所有成员注册吗？</div>
      <div class="answer">是的。注册系统仅对领队开放，领队负责填写成员相关信息。</div>      
      <div class="question">Does the Head Delegate have to register on behalf of all team members?</div>
      <div class="answer">Yes. The registration system has been designed to allow the Head Delegate to take responsibility for his/her delegates.</div>      
      <div class="question">领队如何提交报名表格？</div>
      <div class="answer">请各代表团领队登入网页平台，完成填写代表团全体成员的相关信息，并通过网页提交。</div>      
      <div class="question">How does the Head Delegate submit the application form?</div>
      <div class="answer">The Head Delegate should log in to the system, fill in the information of all team members accurately and submit the application form through the website.</div>      
      <div class="question">我是否可以和另外一所高校的同学组队报名参加？</div>
      <div class="answer">我们强烈建议报名代表与同一所高校的同学组队，以便于日后沟通及合作；同时，我们也将接受跨校的双代表队伍报名。具体操作流程请联系代表联系总监。</div>      
      <div class="question">Can I form a delegation with a person from another school?</div>
      <div class="answer">We strongly suggest delegates to form delegation with people from their own school in order to facilitate communication and cooperation. At the same time, we will also accept registration of double delegation from different schools.Please contact the Director of Delegate Liaison for the application procedures.</div>      
      <div class="question">报名的截止日期是什么时候？</div>
      <div class="answer">代表团报名截止日期为 2019年10月29日。</div>      
      <div class="question">When is the deadline for registration?</div>
      <div class="answer">The deadline for registration is 23:59 (GMT+8),  29 October 2019.</div>      
      <div class="question">提交报名表后多久能得到回复？</div>
      <div class="answer">我们会尽力在5个工作日内予以回复。如申请表格提交一周后如未收到报名成功的确认邮件，请及时与我们取得联系，避免报名失效，错失名额。</div>      
      <div class="question">When can I expect to get a reply after submitting the application form?</div>
      <div class="answer">We will try our best to reply within 5 working days. If you have not received the confirmation email within one week after submitting the application form, please contact us in time to avoid invalid registration.</div>      
      <div class="question">先报名的代表团会被优先录取吗？</div>
      <div class="answer">报名顺序在一定程度上可能影响录取情况，建议尽早报名。录取情况还将取决于其他因素，包括但不限于代表团人数。</div>      
      <div class="question">Will delegates who register first be accepted first?</div>
      <div class="answer">We encourage all delegates to register early as the order of registration may affect admission. However, admission also depends on other factors including but not limited to the size of the delegation.</div>      
      <div class="question">有模联经验的申请者会被优先录取吗？</div>
      <div class="answer">我们坚信，模联是促进跨文化交流和加深现代青年对国际事务和外交的了解的重要途径，任何同学都应该有机会感受并受惠于模联。因此，PICMUN 2019组委在录取代表时不会以是否有模联经验作为唯一标准。但因某些委员会有人数限制或议题较为专业化，PICMUN 2019组委在给这些委员会分配代表时也会将其参会经验等因素纳入考量范围。</div>     
      <div class="question">Will delegates with MUN experience be accepted first?</div>
      <div class="answer">We firmly believe that MUN is a great way to foster cross-culture communication and enhance youths’ understanding of international affairs and diplomacy, and that all students should have the chance to experience and benefit from MUN. Therefore, while processing registrations, the PICMUN team will not discriminate delegates based on their MUN experience (or lack thereof). However, as certain committees have size or other technical constraints, PICMUN will take a variety of factors, including MUN experience, when allocating countries and committees.</div>
      <div class="question">提交报名表格后，领队是否能对报名信息进行修改？</div>
      <div class="answer">报名成功后，各领队将收到确认报名邮件，请各代表团领队确认报名信息准确无误，如需作出任何更改，请在网页上选择修改。但如有不可抗因素导致必须更换代表团成员，请直接与本会代表联系总监联系。</div>
      <div class="question">Can the Head Delegate modify the information after the application form is submitted?</div>
      <div class="answer">After registration, the Head Delegate will receive an email confirming the registration of his/her delegation. If any changes need to be made, please modify the information on the website. If you need to change the delegation members due to force majeure, please contact the Director of Delegation Liaison directly.</div>
      <div class="question">如果被告知未能录取，应该怎么办？</div>
      <div class="answer">由于代表席位数量有限，我们不能保证每一位报名PICMUN的高校同学都被录取。如果被告知未录取，还请您谅解。您也可以通过PICMUN网站和微信平台关注会议进程。</div>
      <div class="question">If I am informed that my registration has not been successful, what should I do?</div>
      <div class="answer">As seats are limited, not all registrations to PICMUN are guaranteed to be successful. If you have been informed that your registration has not been successful, we seek your understanding. You may continue to follow AIMUN through our WeChat platform or website.</div>
      <div class="question">在使用网上报名系统时出现问题怎么办？</div>
      <div class="answer"><p>如果代表团来自中国大陆，领队请联系contact@aimun.org.cn。</p><p>如果代表团来自其他国家及地区，领队请联系 community@aimun.org.cn。</p></div>
      <div class="question">What should I do if I am having trouble with the online registration form?</div>
      <div class="answer"><p>Delegates from mainland China, please have your Head Delegate contact contact@aimun.org.cn.</p><p>Delegates from all other countries and regions, please have your Head Delegate contact community@aimun.org.cn.</p></div>
      <div class="question">指导老师和观察员的注册报名什么时候开始？</div>
      <div class="answer">PICMUN会在2019年10月18日至11月18日接受指导老师和观察员的注册报名。具体报名程序请发电邮到contact@aimun.org.cn进行查询。</div>
      <div class="question">When can faculty advisors/observers register?</div>
      <div class="answer">PICMUN will start receiving application for faculty advisors/observers starting from 18 October 2019 to 18 November 2019. Please email contact@aimun.org.cn for further application details.</div>
    </div>
