      <div class="question">What should I do if I was not assigned the committee that I wanted?</div>
      <div class="answer">As we may receive many registrations and we have size restrictions for a number of our committees, some delegates may not be assigned the committee of their first choice. This is why in the registration form, applicants are asked to select their second and third choice committees. If applicants do not select these options, they may not be accepted. We seek your understanding in this.</div>
