      <div class="title"><p>关于费用</p><p>Conference fees</p></div>
      <div class="question">PICMUN的会费是多少？</div>
      <div class="answer">PICMUN 2019的会费标准为：参会代表人民币240 元，指导老师或观察员人民币180 元。如需会费发票，应额外缴纳5.6%的税费，即每位代表应支付255元（240元不含税费），每位指导教师、观察员应支付190元（180元不含税费）。如需发票，请在报名表格上标记告知。</div>
      <div class="question">What are the conference fees for PICMUN 2019 like?</div>
      <div class="answer">Delegates pay 240 CNY, while faculty advisors and observers pay 180 CNY. Delegates who require an invoice will be required to pay 5.6% of tax. Conference fee with invoice for delegates is 255 CNY, while faculty advisors and observers pay 190 CNY.</div>
      <div class="question">费用包含什么？</div>
      <div class="answer">费用包含会场费用、会务用品以及会议期间茶歇。费用不包含餐饮、住宿、往返交通等其他费用。</div>
      <div class="question">What do the fees cover?</div>
      <div class="answer">The fees cover venue charges, conference materials as well as finger food and drinks for the duration of the conference. The fees do NOT cover regular meals, accommodation, and transport.</div>
      <div class="question">如何缴纳会费？</div>
      <div class="answer">可使用支付宝（推荐）或是银行转账缴费，具体步骤请根据报名平台的具体的指引进行，或具体询问代表联系总监。</div>
      <div class="question">How do I pay the fees?</div>
      <div class="answer">You may use Alipay (recommended) or bank transfer to make the payment. For more details, please refer to the instructions on the registration platform, or contact our Director of Delegate Liaison.</div>
      <div class="question">如何确认会费缴纳成功了？</div>
      <div class="answer">在领队完成缴纳会费之后，请于报名平台上传缴费凭证，代表联系总监确认会费缴纳成功后，网站将显示成功缴费的状态。</div>
      <div class="question">How do I know if my payment has been successful?</div>
      <div class="answer">After paying, please upload the payment vouchers to the registration platform. The platform will display the status of successful payment after confirmation by our Director of Delegate Liaison.</div>
      <div class="question">如果确认被录取后，最终未参加PICMUN 2019，能返还会费吗？</div>
      <div class="answer">2019年11月8日前，代表可申请退费，将会收到全额退款，但其所在学校将失去该名额。2019年11月8日至11月17日，申请退出的代表将被退还50%的费用，其所在学校将失去该名额。2019年11月17日之后，申请退出的代表将不会被退还任何费用，其所在学校将失去该名额。</div>
      <div class="question">Will I be able to get a refund if I am not able to come for PICMUN 2019 in the end?</div>
      <div class="answer">Delegates may request a full refund at any time before 8 November 2019. However upon doing so, the school delegation will lose that slot as a result. Delegates who request for refunds after 8 November 2019, will be refunded 50% of the amount paid. However upon doing so, the school delegation will lose that slot as a result. Delegates who request for refunds after 17 November 2019, will not be refunded any amount, the school delegation will lose that slot as well. Please ensure that you are able to commit to PICMUN 2019 before you sign up for it.</div>
